                    how to find it anymore? Now you won't ever need to comment "what is ____ at 4:43?" 
                    Follow the steps below and and find out!
                </h6>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="container">
            <div class="divider"></div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="section">
            <!--   Icon Section   -->
            <div class="row">

                <div class="col s12 m4">
                    <div class="icon-block">
                        <h2 class="center light-blue-text"><i class="material-icons">subscriptions</i></h2>
                        <h5 class="center">Choose Any YouTube Video</h5>

                        <p class="light">
                            Choose from any of YouTube's millions of videos. Easily get what you are looking
                            for by just pasting the video URL above and Go!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col s12 m4">
                    <div class="icon-block">
                        <h2 class="center light-blue-text"><i class="material-icons">wallpaper</i></h2>
                        <h5 class="center">Capture the Video Screen</h5>

                        <p class="light">
                            Easily find the exact scene you want using a timestamp. Or, if you dont remember,
                            watch the video to find the part you want to know more about and press capture to
                            screenshot what you see.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col s12 m4">
                    <div class="icon-block">
                        <h2 class="center light-blue-text"><i class="material-icons">check_circle</i></h2>
                        <h5 class="center">View Analysis & Search Results</h5>

                        <p class="light">
                            Can't make sense of what you are seeing or want to learn more? Click on the
                            Analyze or Search buttons to find out which show or movie a clip is from or 
                            any webpages that contain that same image!
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
